      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Finally, the size factor, SMB, is constructed by going long the nine small portfolios and short the nine large portfolios. "
      ],
      "id": "c7cc4e9c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "factors_size = (\n",
